    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "well i guess its hard to say since everyone has their own data. but like, when people talk about it being \"unconstitutional,\" isnt that just an opinion? like, the statistics on crime are actual numbers, whereas the 2nd amendment thing is just how people interpret a sentence in a document. wouldn't the data be a more \"real\" way to look at it?",
